{"type":"text","timestamp":1775883974974,"sessionID":"ses_28513bda5ffeehTcJe2NOV9gIv","part":{"id":"prt_d7aecf558001DR6QgzWT4lrZiz","messageID":"msg_d7aece2b200133pupgVAJDb40G","sessionID":"ses_28513bda5ffeehTcJe2NOV9gIv","type":"text","text":"Now I'll write a comprehensive design.md for AR-030:","time":{"start":1775883974971,"end":1775883974971}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775883975156,"sessionID":"ses_28513bda5ffeehTcJe2NOV9gIv","part":{"id":"prt_d7aeef93f0015rZA6VKXX2OP0u","messageID":"msg_d7aece2b200133pupgVAJDb40G","sessionID":"ses_28513bda5ffeehTcJe2NOV9gIv","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-fe8746efccf7477c9e9b21ba5a240be6","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-030/design.md","content":"# AR-030 — Helm Chart 模板与 Values Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-030 — Helm Chart 模板与 Values |\n| Module | `manifests` |\n| Language | YAML |\n| Size | L |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\nDefine the official Helm Chart for AgentCube deployment, providing parameterized Kubernetes manifests for all core components (workloadmanager, router, agentd, redis) with configurable values for image registry, replicas, resources, and environment-specific overrides.\n\n---\n\n## Architecture\n\n### High-Level Architecture\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                         Helm Chart Structure                                 │\n│                     manifests/charts/base/                                   │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│                                                                              │\n│  ┌──────────────────┐    ┌──────────────────┐    ┌──────────────────┐      │\n│  │   Chart.yaml     │    │   values.yaml    │    │  templates/_*    │      │\n│  │  (Metadata)      │───▶│  (Config)        │───▶│  (Rendered YAML) │      │\n│  └──────────────────┘    └──────────────────┘    └──────────────────┘      │\n│                                                                              │\n│  Templates:                                                                  │\n│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐    │\n│  │ workloadmanager.yaml        │ Deployment + Service                   │    │\n│  │ agentcube-router.yaml       │ Deployment + Service                   │    │\n│  │ rbac/workloadmanager.yaml   │ SA, ClusterRole, ClusterRoleBinding   │    │\n│  │ rbac-router.yaml            │ SA, Role, RoleBinding (conditional)   │    │\n│  │ volcano-agent-scheduler     │ Scheduler resources (conditional)      │    │\n│  │ _helpers.tpl                │ Named template helpers                 │    │\n│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘    │\n│                                                                              │\n│  CRDs (crds/):                                                               │\n│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐    │\n│  │ runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml                      │    │\n│  │ runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml                   │    │\n│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘    │\n│                                                                              │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n### Deployment Model\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                      Kubernetes Cluster                                       │\n│                      Namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}                     │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│                                                                              │\n│  ┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │\n│  │                    AgentCube Components                                 │ │\n│  ├────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤ │\n│  │                                                                         │ │\n│  │  ┌───────────────────┐         ┌───────────────────┐                  │ │\n│  │  │ workloadmanager   │         │ agentcube-router  │                  │ │\n│  │  │ Deployment        │◀───────▶│ Deployment        │                  │ │\n│  │  │ (replicas: 1)     │         │ (replicas: 1)     │                  │ │\n│  │  │ Port: 8080        │         │ Port: 8080        │                  │ │\n│  │  └───────────────────┘         └───────────────────┘                  │ │\n│  │          │                              │                              │ │\n│  │          │                              │                              │ │\n│  │          ▼                              ▼                              │ │\n│  │  ┌───────────────────┐         ┌───────────────────┐                  │ │\n│  │  │ workloadmanager   │         │ agentcube-router  │                  │ │\n│  │  │ Service (ClusterIP│         │ Service (ClusterIP│                  │ │\n│  │  │  port: 8080)      │         │  port: 8080)      │                  │ │\n│  │  └───────────────────┘         └───────────────────┘                  │ │\n│  │                                                                         │ │\n│  │  ┌───────────────────┐                                                │ │\n│  │  │ redis Deployment  │    (if enabled, external or bundled)          │ │\n│  │  │ redis Service     │                                                │ │\n│  │  │ Port: 6379        │                                                │ │\n│  │  └───────────────────┘                                                │ │\n│  │                                                                         │ │\n│  │  ┌───────────────────┐                                                │ │\n│  │  │ volcano-agent-    │    (if volcano.scheduler.enabled)             │ │\n│  │  │ scheduler         │                                                │ │\n│  │  └───────────────────┘                                                │ │\n│  │                                                                         │ │\n│  └────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │\n│                                                                              │\n│  ┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │\n│  │                    RBAC Resources                                       │ │\n│  ├────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤ │\n│  │  ServiceAccount: workloadmanager (cluster-scoped)                      │ │\n│  │  ServiceAccount: agentcube-router (namespace-scoped, conditional)      │ │\n│  │  ServiceAccount: volcano-agent-scheduler (cluster-scoped, conditional) │ │\n│  └────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │\n│                                                                              │\n│  ┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │\n│  │                    Secrets                                              │ │\n│  ├────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤ │\n│  │  jwt-secret: JWT signing key (optional)                                │ │\n│  │  identity-secret: Picod-Router identity (optional)                     │ │\n│  └────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │\n│                                                                              │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n### Component Relationships\n\n| Component | Role | Dependencies |\n|-----------|------|--------------|\n| `Chart.yaml` | Chart metadata (name, version, appVersion) | None |\n| `values.yaml` | Default configuration values | Chart.yaml (version reference) |\n| `_helpers.tpl` | Named template helpers (name, fullname, labels) | values.yaml |\n| `workloadmanager.yaml` | WorkloadManager Deployment + Service | values.yaml, _helpers.tpl |\n| `agentcube-router.yaml` | Router Deployment + Service | values.yaml, _helpers.tpl, workloadmanager Service |\n| `rbac/workloadmanager.yaml` | RBAC for WorkloadManager | _helpers.tpl, workloadmanager.yaml |\n| `rbac-router.yaml` | RBAC for Router (conditional) | _helpers.tpl, agentcube-router.yaml |\n| `volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` | Volcano scheduler (conditional) | values.yaml, _helpers.tpl |\n| `crds/*.yaml` | CRD definitions (installed before templates) | controller-gen |\n\n---\n\n## Data Structures\n\n### Chart.yaml Schema\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: v1\nname: agentcube\ndescription: A Helm chart for AgentCube\ntype: application\nversion: 0.1.0        # Chart version (SemVer 2)\nappVersion: 1.0.0     # Application version\nkeywords:\n  - agentcube\n  - kubernetes\n  - sandbox\n  - ai-agents\nmaintainers:\n  - name: volcano-sh\n    email: volcano-sh@example.com\nsources:\n  - https://github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube\n```\n\n### values.yaml Schema\n\n```yaml\n# Global settings\nimagePullSecrets: []           # array[string] - Secret names for private registries\nnameOverride: \"\"               # string - Partial name override\nfullnameOverride: \"\"           # string - Full name override\n\n# Redis connection (must be provided by user)\nredis:\n  addr: \"\"                     # string - Redis address (host:port)\n  password: \"\"                 # string - Redis password (empty = no auth)\n\n# WorkloadManager configuration\nworkloadmanager:\n  replicas: 1                  # int - Deployment replicas\n  image:\n    repository: ghcr.io/volcano-sh/workloadmanager\n    pullPolicy: IfNotPresent\n    tag: latest\n  service:\n    type: ClusterIP\n    port: 8080\n  resources:\n    limits:\n      cpu: 500m\n      memory: 512Mi\n    requests:\n      cpu: 100m\n      memory: 128Mi\n  extraEnv: []                 # array[object] - Extra environment variables\n\n# Router configuration\nrouter:\n  replicas: 1\n  image:\n    repository: ghcr.io/volcano-sh/agentcube-router\n    pullPolicy: IfNotPresent\n    tag: latest\n  service:\n    type: ClusterIP\n    port: 8080\n    targetPort: 8080\n  resources:\n    limits:\n      cpu: 500m\n      memory: 512Mi\n    requests:\n      cpu: 100m\n      memory: 128Mi\n  config: {}                   # object - Router configuration\n  extraEnv: []                 # array[object] - Extra environment variables\n  serviceAccountName: \"\"       # string - ServiceAccount name (empty = default)\n  rbac:\n    create: false              # bool - Create RBAC resources\n\n# Volcano scheduler (optional)\nvolcano:\n  scheduler:\n    enabled: false             # bool - Enable Volcano agent scheduler\n    replicas: 1\n    image:\n      repository: ghcr.io/volcano-sh/vc-agent-scheduler\n      pullPolicy: IfNotPresent\n      tag: latest\n```\n\n### Values Type Definitions\n\n| Path | Type | Default | Description |\n|------|------|---------|-------------|\n| `imagePullSecrets` | `array[string]` | `[]` | Secret names for private registries |\n| `nameOverride` | `string` | `\"\"` | Partial name override |\n| `fullnameOverride` | `string` | `\"\"` | Full name override |\n| `redis.addr` | `string` | `\"\"` | Redis address (`host:port`) |\n| `redis.password` | `string` | `\"\"` | Redis password |\n| `router.replicas` | `int` | `1` | Router deployment replicas |\n| `router.image.repository` | `string` | `ghcr.io/volcano-sh/agentcube-router` | Router image repository |\n| `router.image.pullPolicy` | `string` | `IfNotPresent` | Image pull policy |\n| `router.image.tag` | `string` | `latest` | Router image tag |\n| `router.service.type` | `string` | `ClusterIP` | Router service type |\n| `router.service.port` | `int` | `8080` | Router service port |\n| `router.service.targetPort` | `int` | `8080` | Router container port |\n| `router.resources.limits.cpu` | `string` | `500m` | CPU limit |\n| `router.resources.limits.memory` | `string` | `512Mi` | Memory limit |\n| `router.resources.requests.cpu` | `string` | `100m` | CPU request |\n| `router.resources.requests.memory` | `string` | `128Mi` | Memory request |\n| `router.serviceAccountName` | `string` | `\"\"` | ServiceAccount name |\n| `router.rbac.create` | `bool` | `false` | Create Router RBAC |\n| `workloadmanager.replicas` | `int` | `1` | WorkloadManager replicas |\n| `workloadmanager.image.repository` | `string` | `ghcr.io/volcano-sh/workloadmanager` | WorkloadManager image |\n| `workloadmanager.service.port` | `int` | `8080` | WorkloadManager service port |\n| `volcano.scheduler.enabled` | `bool` | `false` | Enable Volcano scheduler |\n\n### Named Templates (_helpers.tpl)\n\n```yaml\n{{- define \"agentcube.name\" -}}\n{{- default .Chart.Name .Values.nameOverride | trunc 63 | trimSuffix \"-\" -}}\n{{- end -}}\n\n{{- define \"agentcube.fullname\" -}}\n{{- if .Values.fullnameOverride -}}\n{{- .Values.fullnameOverride | trunc 63 | trimSuffix \"-\" -}}\n{{- else -}}\n{{- $name := default .Chart.Name .Values.nameOverride -}}\n{{- if contains $name .Release.Name -}}\n{{- .Release.Name | trunc 63 | trimSuffix \"-\" -}}\n{{- else -}}\n{{- printf \"%s-%s\" .Release.Name $name | trunc 63 | trimSuffix \"-\" -}}\n{{- end -}}\n{{- end -}}\n{{- end -}}\n\n{{- define \"agentcube.labels\" -}}\napp.kubernetes.io/name: {{ include \"agentcube.name\" . }}\napp.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}\napp.kubernetes.io/version: {{ .Chart.AppVersion }}\napp.kubernetes.io/managed-by: {{ .Release.Service }}\n{{- end -}}\n\n{{- define \"agentcube.selectorLabels\" -}}\napp: {{ include \"agentcube.name\" . }}\n{{- end -}}\n\n{{- define \"agentcube.image\" -}}\n{{- $registry := .Values.global.imageRegistry | default \"\" -}}\n{{- $repository := .repository -}}\n{{- $tag := .tag | default \"latest\" -}}\n{{- if $registry -}}\n{{- printf \"%s/%s:%s\" $registry $repository $tag -}}\n{{- else -}}\n{{- printf \"%s:%s\" $repository $tag -}}\n{{- end -}}\n{{- end -}}\n```\n\n---\n\n## API Contracts\n\n### WorkloadManager Deployment Template\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: apps/v1\nkind: Deployment\nmetadata:\n  name: workloadmanager\n  namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}\n  labels:\n    {{- include \"agentcube.labels\" . | nindent 4 }}\nspec:\n  replicas: {{ .Values.workloadmanager.replicas }}\n  selector:\n    matchLabels:\n      {{- include \"agentcube.selectorLabels\" . | nindent 6 }}\n      app: workloadmanager\n  template:\n    metadata:\n      labels:\n        {{- include \"agentcube.selectorLabels\" . | nindent 8 }}\n        app: workloadmanager\n    spec:\n      serviceAccountName: workloadmanager\n      {{- with .Values.imagePullSecrets }}\n      imagePullSecrets:\n        {{- toYaml . | nindent 8 }}\n      {{- end }}\n      containers:\n        - name: workloadmanager\n          image: \"{{ .Values.workloadmanager.image.repository }}:{{ .Values.workloadmanager.image.tag }}\"\n          imagePullPolicy: {{ .Values.workloadmanager.image.pullPolicy }}\n          ports:\n            - name: http\n              containerPort: {{ .Values.workloadmanager.service.port }}\n              protocol: TCP\n          env:\n            - name: AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE\n              valueFrom:\n                fieldRef:\n                  fieldPath: metadata.namespace\n            - name: REDIS_PASSWORD\n              value: \"{{ .Values.redis.password }}\"\n            - name: REDIS_ADDR\n              value: \"{{ .Values.redis.addr }}\"\n            {{- with .Values.workloadmanager.extraEnv }}\n            {{- toYaml . | nindent 12 }}\n            {{- end }}\n          args:\n            - --port={{ .Values.workloadmanager.service.port }}\n            - --runtime-class-name=\n          resources:\n            {{- toYaml .Values.workloadmanager.resources | nindent 12 }}\n          livenessProbe:\n            httpGet:\n              path: /health\n              port: {{ .Values.workloadmanager.service.port }}\n            initialDelaySeconds: 10\n            periodSeconds: 10\n          readinessProbe:\n            httpGet:\n              path: /health\n              port: {{ .Values.workloadmanager.service.port }}\n            initialDelaySeconds: 5\n            periodSeconds: 5\n```\n\n### WorkloadManager Service Template\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: v1\nkind: Service\nmetadata:\n  name: workloadmanager\n  namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}\n  labels:\n    {{- include \"agentcube.labels\" . | nindent 4 }}\nspec:\n  type: {{ .Values.workloadmanager.service.type }}\n  ports:\n    - port: {{ .Values.workloadmanager.service.port }}\n      targetPort: {{ .Values.workloadmanager.service.port }}\n      protocol: TCP\n      name: http\n  selector:\n    app: workloadmanager\n```\n\n### Router Deployment Template\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: apps/v1\nkind: Deployment\nmetadata:\n  name: agentcube-router\n  namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}\n  labels:\n    {{- include \"agentcube.labels\" . | nindent 4 }}\nspec:\n  replicas: {{ .Values.router.replicas }}\n  selector:\n    matchLabels:\n      app: agentcube-router\n  template:\n    metadata:\n      labels:\n        app: agentcube-router\n    spec:\n      {{- if .Values.router.serviceAccountName }}\n      serviceAccountName: {{ .Values.router.serviceAccountName }}\n      {{- end }}\n      {{- with .Values.imagePullSecrets }}\n      imagePullSecrets:\n        {{- toYaml . | nindent 8 }}\n      {{- end }}\n      containers:\n        - name: agentcube-router\n          image: \"{{ .Values.router.image.repository }}:{{ .Values.router.image.tag }}\"\n          imagePullPolicy: {{ .Values.router.image.pullPolicy }}\n          ports:\n            - name: http\n              containerPort: {{ .Values.router.service.targetPort }}\n              protocol: TCP\n          env:\n            - name: AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE\n              valueFrom:\n                fieldRef:\n                  fieldPath: metadata.namespace\n            - name: REDIS_ADDR\n              value: \"{{ .Values.redis.addr }}\"\n            - name: REDIS_PASSWORD\n              value: \"{{ .Values.redis.password }}\"\n            - name: WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL\n              value: \"http://workloadmanager.{{ .Release.Namespace }}.svc.cluster.local:{{ .Values.workloadmanager.service.port }}\"\n            {{- with .Values.router.extraEnv }}\n            {{- toYaml . | nindent 12 }}\n            {{- end }}\n          args:\n            - --port={{ .Values.router.service.targetPort }}\n            - --debug\n          resources:\n            {{- toYaml .Values.router.resources | nindent 12 }}\n          livenessProbe:\n            httpGet:\n              path: /health/live\n              port: {{ .Values.router.service.targetPort }}\n            initialDelaySeconds: 1\n            periodSeconds: 2\n          readinessProbe:\n            httpGet:\n              path: /health/ready\n              port: {{ .Values.router.service.targetPort }}\n            initialDelaySeconds: 1\n            periodSeconds: 2\n```\n\n### Router Service Template\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: v1\nkind: Service\nmetadata:\n  name: agentcube-router\n  namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}\n  labels:\n    {{- include \"agentcube.labels\" . | nindent 4 }}\nspec:\n  type: {{ .Values.router.service.type }}\n  ports:\n    - port: {{ .Values.router.service.port }}\n      targetPort: {{ .Values.router.service.targetPort }}\n      protocol: TCP\n      name: http\n  selector:\n    app: agentcube-router\n```\n\n---\n\n## Error Handling\n\n### Template Validation Errors\n\n| Error Type | Cause | Resolution |\n|------------|-------|------------|\n| `Helm lint error` | Invalid YAML syntax or missing required fields | Fix template syntax, add required fields |\n| `Render error` | Undefined template reference or invalid values path | Check helper template names, validate values paths |\n| `Missing value` | Required value not provided | Set required values in values.yaml or via `--set` |\n| `Invalid resource spec` | Kubernetes API schema violation | Validate against Kubernetes API schema |\n\n### Validation Patterns\n\n```yaml\n{{- if not .Values.redis.addr }}\n{{- fail \"redis.addr must be provided\" }}\n{{- end }}\n\n{{- if .Values.router.rbac.create }}\n{{- if not .Values.router.serviceAccountName }}\n{{- fail \"router.serviceAccountName must be set when router.rbac.create is true\" }}\n{{- end }}\n{{- end }}\n```\n\n### Conditional Rendering\n\n```yaml\n{{- if .Values.router.rbac.create }}\n# RBAC resources rendered\n{{- end }}\n\n{{- if .Values.volcano.scheduler.enabled }}\n# Volcano scheduler resources rendered\n{{- end }}\n\n{{- with .Values.imagePullSecrets }}\nimagePullSecrets:\n  {{- toYaml . | nindent 8 }}\n{{- end }}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n### Test Categories\n\n| Category | Scope | Tools |\n|----------|-------|-------|\n| Helm lint | Chart syntax validation | `helm lint manifests/charts/base` |\n| Template render | YAML output validation | `helm template agentcube manifests/charts/base` |\n| Values override | Custom values integration | `helm template ... -f custom-values.yaml` |\n| E2E deployment | Full stack deployment | `helm upgrade --install ... --wait` |\n| CRD validation | CRD schema compliance | `kubectl apply --dry-run=client` |\n\n### Helm Lint Tests\n\n```bash\nhelm lint manifests/charts/base\n# Expected: 0 errors, 0 warnings\n```\n\n### Template Render Tests\n\n```bash\nhelm template agentcube manifests/charts/base \\\n  --set redis.addr=\"redis.default.svc.cluster.local:6379\" \\\n  --set redis.password=\"\" \\\n  > /tmp/rendered.yaml\n\n# Validate rendered YAML\nkubectl apply --dry-run=client -f /tmp/rendered.yaml\n```\n\n### Values Override Tests\n\n```yaml\n# test-values.yaml\nredis:\n  addr: \"redis.test.svc.cluster.local:6379\"\n  password: \"test-password\"\nrouter:\n  replicas: 2\n  rbac:\n    create: true\n  serviceAccountName: \"test-router-sa\"\nworkloadmanager:\n  replicas: 3\n  extraEnv:\n    - name: TEST_ENV\n      value: \"test-value\"\n```\n\n```bash\nhelm template agentcube manifests/charts/base -f test-values.yaml\n```\n\n### E2E Integration Test\n\n```bash\nhelm upgrade --install agentcube manifests/charts/base \\\n  --namespace agentcube \\\n  --create-namespace \\\n  --set redis.addr=\"redis.agentcube.svc.cluster.local:6379\" \\\n  --set redis.password=\"\" \\\n  --set workloadmanager.image.repository=\"workloadmanager\" \\\n  --set workloadmanager.image.tag=\"latest\" \\\n  --set-json 'workloadmanager.extraEnv=[{\"name\":\"REDIS_PASSWORD_REQUIRED\",\"value\":\"false\"}]' \\\n  --set router.image.repository=\"agentcube-router\" \\\n  --set router.image.tag=\"latest\" \\\n  --set router.rbac.create=true \\\n  --set router.serviceAccountName=\"agentcube-router\" \\\n  --wait\n```\n\n### Test Matrix\n\n| Test Case | Values Override | Expected Output |\n|-----------|-----------------|-----------------|\n| Default values | None | All components enabled with defaults |\n| Router RBAC enabled | `router.rbac.create=true` | Router RBAC resources rendered |\n| Volcano scheduler enabled | `volcano.scheduler.enabled=true` | Scheduler resources rendered |\n| Custom replicas | `router.replicas=3` | Router Deployment spec.replicas=3 |\n| Custom resources | `router.resources.limits.cpu=1` | CPU limit overridden |\n| Extra environment | `router.extraEnv=[{...}]` | Additional env vars rendered |\n| Image override | `router.image.tag=v1.0.0` | Custom image tag used |\n\n---\n\n## File Structure\n\n| Path | Role |\n|------|------|\n| `manifests/charts/base/Chart.yaml` | Chart metadata (name, version, appVersion) |\n| `manifests/charts/base/values.yaml` | Default configuration values |\n| `manifests/charts/base/templates/_helpers.tpl` | Named template helpers |\n| `manifests/charts/base/templates/workloadmanager.yaml` | WorkloadManager Deployment + Service |\n| `manifests/charts/base/templates/agentcube-router.yaml` | Router Deployment + Service |\n| `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml` | WorkloadManager RBAC (SA, ClusterRole, ClusterRoleBinding) |\n| `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac-router.yaml` | Router RBAC (SA, Role, RoleBinding - conditional) |\n| `manifests/charts/base/templates/volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` | Volcano scheduler (conditional) |\n| `manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml` | AgentRuntime CRD |\n| `manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml` | CodeInterpreter CRD |\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n| Package | Version | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|---------|\n| `Helm 3` | `>=3.8.0` | Template rendering and release management |\n| `Kubernetes` | `>=1.24` | API versions for Deployment, Service, RBAC, CRD |\n| `controller-gen` | `v0.17.2` | CRD generation from Go types |\n| `agent-sandbox CRDs` | `v0.1.1` | Sandbox CRDs from sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox |\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Notes\n\n### RBAC Rules\n\n#### WorkloadManager ClusterRole\n\n| apiGroups | resources | verbs |\n|-----------|-----------|-------|\n| `agents.x-k8s.io` | `sandboxes` | `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete` |\n| `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io` | `sandboxclaims`, `sandboxtemplates`, `sandboxwarmpools` | `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete` |\n| `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io` | `sandboxwarmpools/status` | `get,update,patch` |\n| `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` | `codeinterpreters` | `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete` |\n| `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` | `codeinterpreters/status` | `get,update,patch` |\n| `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` | `codeinterpreters/finalizers` | `update` |\n| `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` | `agentruntimes` | `get,list,watch` |\n| `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` | `agentruntimes/status` | `update,patch` |\n| `\"\"` (core) | `pods` | `get,list,watch` |\n| `authentication.k8s.io` | `tokenreviews` | `create` |\n| `\"\"` (core) | `secrets` | `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete` |\n\n#### Router Role (namespace-scoped)\n\n| apiGroups | resources | verbs |\n|-----------|-----------|-------|\n| `\"\"` | `secrets` | `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete` |\n\n### Health Probes\n\n| Component | Liveness Path | Readiness Path | Initial Delay | Period |\n|-----------|---------------|----------------|---------------|--------|\n| WorkloadManager | `/health` | `/health` | 10s / 5s | 10s / 5s |\n| Router | `/health/live` | `/health/ready` | 1s | 2s |\n\n### Environment Variables\n\n| Variable | Source | Component |\n|----------|--------|-----------|\n| `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE` | `fieldRef: metadata.namespace` | Router, WorkloadManager |\n| `REDIS_ADDR` | `.Values.redis.addr` | Router, WorkloadManager |\n| `REDIS_PASSWORD` | `.Values.redis.password` | Router, WorkloadManager |\n| `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` | Constructed from release namespace | Router |\n\n### CRD Schema\n\n#### AgentRuntime CRD\n\n| Field | Type | Default | Required |\n|-------|------|---------|----------|\n| `maxSessionDuration` | string | `8h` | Yes |\n| `sessionTimeout` | string | `15m` | Yes |\n| `podTemplate` | object | - | Yes |\n| `targetPort` | array | - | Yes |\n\n#### CodeInterpreter CRD\n\n| Field | Type | Default | Required |\n|-------|------|---------|----------|\n| `authMode` | enum (`picod`, `none`) | `picod` | No |\n| `maxSessionDuration` | string | `8h` | No |\n| `sessionTimeout` | string | `15m` | No |\n| `template` | object | - | Yes |\n| `warmPoolSize` | int32 | - | No |\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- Spec: `changes/AR-030/spec.md`\n- Delta Spec: `changes/AR-030/delta-spec.md`\n- Proposal: `changes/AR-030/proposal.md`\n- Tasks: `changes/AR-030/tasks.md`\n- deployment/design.md — Reference implementation details\n- ci-cd/design.md — E2E Helm usage patterns\n- project.md — AgentCube project context\n- Helm 3 Documentation — Chart structure, templates, values best practices\n- Kubernetes API Reference — Deployment, Service, RBAC schemas"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/